### Variables
@HostUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Set Permission - Set folder permissions for a user
POST {{HostUrl}}/api/folders/1/permissions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "canRead": true,
  "canWrite": true,
  "canDelete": false,
  "canManagePermissions": false,
  "grantedByUserId": 1
}

###

